# Old Bay Sauce

![](7DAA5B3F-80BF-4176-B5A8-EA3435E8A654.jpg)

## Ingredients

- Mayonnaise | 1/2 cup | 
- Greek Yogurt | 1/2 cup sour cream or plain | 
- Lemon Juice | 1 tablespoon | 
- Pickle Relish | 1 tablespoon dill | 
- Old Bay Seasoning | 2 teaspoons | 
- Hot Sauce | 1/2 teaspoon | 

## Instructions

1. Place all ingredients into a bowl and stir to combine. Cover and refrigerate until ready to serve.

